&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Band 5 Cardiac Nurse &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Ward 23 Cardiology - Good Hope Hospital&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are a dynamic, fast moving, innovative cardiac centre with a passion for providing safe care.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;You may be newly qualified, experienced in cardiology or just fancied a new challenge. If you have enthusiasm, commitment and can work as part of a team to deliver exceptional care then we want you. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We can offer you excitement, development and a chance to be your very best. Not to mention being part of a great supportive team. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;It takes a certain person to be able to work in this environment and we need motivated, passionate and hardworking individuals. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you feel this is an opportunity for you then please call us, visit us or apply now. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;For further information or to arrange an informal visit please contact: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Rose Mulvany Senior Sister Ward 23 GHH on 0121 424 7223 / 7467 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Closing date 15&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;th&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; November 2020&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Interviews will be held on 26&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;th&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; November 2020&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span&gt;At University Hospitals Birmingham we support flexible working and welcome applications from nurses seeking flexible working opportunities and family friendly working hours.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
